    modified_response: "I will now create the main entry file `/server.ts` for our Express full-stack application. It implements the API endpoints for order orchestration (CRUD), database testing, the machine learning computations, automatic Google Sheets sync, email triggers, and mounts the Vite middleware to serve our React application seamlessly."
