    modified_response: "I will now create the component `/src/components/AdminPanel.tsx`. This file operates as the primary CRM and Admin Panel for the managers of \"Entre Parrilleros\". It provides:\n1. **Durable CRUD Interface**: Admins can fetch, create custom orders, edit order items/clients/status, or delete records entirely.\n2. **Google Sheets Sync Portal**: Details spreadsheet parameters and exposes manual trigger macros.\n3. **Monthly Sales Report automation**: Aggregates month-over-month revenues, tickets, and shares of meats vs grocery goods utilizing interactive dynamic Recharts charts.\n4. **Connectivity Diagnostics**: Visual indicators revealing real connection health with the local HeidiSQL/Laragon MySQL port."
