    modified_response: "I will now write the main dynamic router and container file `/src/App.tsx`. This component manages the React state (orders list, loading indicator, connection checks, and refreshing counters) and fetches lists from the backend `/api/orders`. It sets up a visually stunning tab switcher styled with warm charcoal tones, embers, and elegant transitions from `motion/react` to orchestrate:\n1. **Portal Clientes**: The \"Entre Parrilleros\" storefront.\n2. **Gesti\303\263n Administrativa**: The CRM, Order CRUD, Google Sheets sync, and Monthly automated CSV exporter.\n3. **Modelos Predictivos (ML)**: The parallel classifier models (Decision Tree & KNN), Pandas metrics, Plotly layout, and f-string injects."
