case tracking-widest font-semibold\\\"><span class=\\\"text-[#b91c1c]\\\">\342\227\217 Live System: Connected</span><span>Cat\303\241logo</span><span>Pedidos</span><span>Admin Console</span></div></header><main class=\\\"flex-1 grid grid-cols-12 gap-0\\\"><section class=\\\"col-span-4 border-r border-white/10 p-8 flex flex-col bg-[#161616]\\\"><div class=\\\"mb-8\\\"><h2 class=\\\"text-2xl font-serif italic mb-2\\\">Gesti\303\263n de Pedidos</h2><p class=\\\"text-sm text-zinc-400\\\">Captura de servicios y sincronizaci\303\263n inmediata con Google Sheets.</p></div><form class=\\\"space-y-4 flex-1\\\"><div class=\\\"space-y-1\\\"><label class=\\\"text-[10px] uppercase tracking-wider text-zinc-500 font-bold\\\">Nombre del Cliente</label><input type=\\\"text\\\" placeholder=\\\"Juan P\303\251rez\\\" class=\\\"w-full bg-zinc-800/50 border border-white/10 px-4 py-3 text-sm focus:outline-none focus:border-[#b91c1c]\\\" readonly></div><div class=\\\"space-y-1\\\"><label class=\\\"text-[10px] uppercase tracking-wider text-zinc-500 font-bold\\\">Servicio / Producto</label><select class=\\\"w-full bg-zinc-800/50 border border-white/10 px-4 py-3 text-sm focus:outline-none appearance-none\\\"><option>Pack Asado Premium - $45.000</option></select></div><div class=\\\"space-y-1\\\"><label class=\\\"text-[10px] uppercase tracking-wider text-zinc-500 font-bold\\\">Notas Especiales</label><textarea rows=\\\"2\\\" class=\\\"w-full bg-zinc-800/50 border border-white/10 px-4 py-3 text-sm focus:outline-none resize-none\\\" readonly>Corte tipo mariposa para la entra\303\261a.</textarea></div><button type=\\\"button\\\" class=\\\"w-full bg-[#b91c1c] py-4 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest hover:bg-red-700 transition-colors mt-4\\\">Confirmar Pedido & Notificar</button></form><div class=\\\"mt-8 pt-6 border-t border-white/5\\\"><div class=\\\"flex justify-between items-center text-[10px] mb-2\\\"><span class=\\\"opacity-50 uppercase\\\">Sync Status</span><span class=\\\"text-green-500 font-bold tracking-widest\\\">GOOGLE SHEETS: OK</span></div><div class=\\\"flex justify-between items-center text-[10px]\\\"><span class=\\\"opacity-50 uppercase\\\">Notifications</span><span class=\\\"text-green-500 font-bold tracking-widest\\\">EMAIL SMTP: ACTIVE</span></div></div></section><section class=\\\"col-span-8 p-10 bg-[#121212] relative overflow-hidden\\\"><div class=\\\"flex justify-between items-start mb-12\\\"><div class=\\\"space-y-1\\\"><h2 class=\\\"text-5xl font-serif italic\\\">Predicciones & M\303\251tricas</h2><p class=\\\"text-zinc-500 tracking-wide\\\">An\303\241lisis de Fuga y Comportamiento (Sucursal: Osorno Centro)</p></div><div class=\\\"bg-white/5 border border-white/10 p-4 rounded-sm\\\"><p class=\\\"text-[10px] uppercase text-zinc-400 mb-1\\\">DB Laragon Instance</p><p class=\\\"font-mono text-xl text-[#b91c1c]\\\">DB: parrillero_vigente</p></div></div><div class=\\\"grid grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-10\\\"><div class=\\\"border-l-2 border-[#b91c1c] pl-4 py-2\\\"> <p class=\\\"text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest text-zinc-500\\\">Registros Vigentes</p><p class=\\\"text-4xl font-light font-mono\\\">1,248</p></div><div class=\\\"border-l-2 border-white/20 pl-4 py-2\\\"> <p class=\\\"text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest text-zinc-500\\\">Score \303\201rbol Decisi\303\263n</p><p class=\\\"text-4xl font-light font-mono text-green-400\\\">0.942</p></div><div class=\\\"border-l-2 border-white/20 pl-4 py-2\\\"> <p class=\\\"text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest text-zinc-500\\\">Score KNN (k=5)</p><p class=\\\"text-4xl font-light font-mono text-green-400\\\">0.887</p></div></div><div class=\\\"h-56 w-full border border-white/10 bg-zinc-900/40 relative flex items-end p-4 gap-2\\\"><div class=\\\"absolute top-4 left-4 flex flex-col gap-1\\\"><p class=\\\"text-[10px] uppercase font-bold tracking-tighter\\\">Relaci\303\263n Gasto vs Visitas (Scatter Plot)</p><div class=\\\"flex gap-3 text-[9px] uppercase\\\"><span class=\\\"flex items-center gap-1\\\"><i class=\\\"w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-red-500\\\"></i> Fuga</span><span class=\\\"flex items-center gap-1\\\"><i class=\\\"w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-green-500\\\"></i> Leal</span></div></div><div class=\\\"w-3 h-12 bg-red-500/40 border border-red-500\\\"></div><div class=\\\"w-3 h-24 bg-green-500/40 border border-green-500\\\"></div><div class=\\\"w-3 h-16 bg-red-500/40 border border-red-500\\\"></div><div class=\\\"w-3 h-32 bg-green-500/40 border border-green-500\\\"></div><div class=\\\"w-3 h-40 bg-green-500/40 border border-green-500\\\"></div><div class=\\\"w-3 h-20 bg-red-500/40 border border-red-500\\\"></div><div class=\\\"w-3 h-48 bg-green-500/40 border border-green-500\\\"></div><div class=\\\"w-3 h-14 bg-red-500/40 border border-red-500\\\"></div><div class=\\\"w-3 h-52 bg-green-500/40 border border-green-500\\\"></div><div class=\\\"w-3 h-22 bg-red-500/40 border border-red-500\\\"></div><div class=\\\"w-3 h-38 bg-green-500/40 border border-green-500\\\"></div><div class=\\\"w-3 h-44 bg-green-500/40 border border-green-500\\\"></div><div class=\\\"w-3 h-28 bg-red-500/40 border border-red-500\\\"></div></div><div class=\\\"mt-8 grid grid-cols-2 gap-8 text-xs\\\"><div class=\\\"bg-white/5 p-4 border border-white/5\\\"><h4 class=\\\"font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-[#b91c1c] mb-2\\\">Sync de Transacciones (Hot Reload)</h4><p class=\\\"opacity-70 leading-relaxed\\\">Para actualizar m\303\251tricas sin recargar: El dashboard ejecuta un polling ligero a la API de SQLAlchemy. Al detectar cambios en el timestamp de la tabla \'ventas\', dispara un script de Pandas que re-entrena los modelos en paralelo y actualiza los f-strings del DOM v\303\255a AJAX.</p></div><div class=\\\"bg-white/5 p-4 border border-white/5 flex flex-col justify-between\\\"><h4 class=\\\"font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-zinc-300 mb-2\\\">Reporte Mensual Automatizado</h4><div class=\\\"flex justify-between items-end\\\"><p class=\\\"opacity-70\\\">Pr\303\263ximo env\303\255o programado: 31 Oct, 23:59</p><button class=\\\"text-[10px] border border-white/20 px-3 py-1 hover:bg-white/10\\\">Descargar PDF</button></div></div></div></section></main><footer class=\\\"bg-black px-10 py-3 flex justify-between items-center border-t border-white/10 text-[9px] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] font-medium opacity-50\\\"><div>\302\251 2024 Entre Parrilleros - Central Intelligence Engine</div><div>Engine v2.4.1 | Osorno Branch Controller</div></footer></div>\\n  </body>\\n</html>\n[AIS_METADATA_SECTION_END]"
