ado: 31 Oct, 23:59</p><button class=\\\"text-[10px] border border-white/20 px-3 py-1 hover:bg-white/10\\\">Descargar PDF</button></div></div></div></section></main><footer class=\\\"bg-black px-10 py-3 flex justify-between items-center border-t border-white/10 text-[9px] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] font-medium opacity-50\\\"><div>\302\251 2024 Entre Parrilleros - Central Intelligence Engine</div><div>Engine v2.4.1 | Osorno Branch Controller</div></footer></div>\\n  </body>\\n</html>\n[AIS_METADATA_SECTION_END]"
