    instruction: "Style MLDashboard outer frame, top headers, help alert, and tabs to match the Editorial Aesthetic theme"
    replacement_infos {
      original_chunk {
        target_content: "  return (\n    <div className=\"bg-neutral-950 text-neutral-100 min-h-screen p-4 md:p-8\">\n      {/* Tab Menu Options */}\n      <div className=\"mx-auto max-w-7xl\">\n        <div className=\"flex flex-col md:flex-row items-start md:items-center justify-between border-b border-neutral-900 pb-5 mb-8 gap-4\">\n          <div>\n            <h1 className=\"text-3xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-neutral-550 flex items-center gap-3\">\n              <TrendingUp className=\"w-8 h-8 text-amber-500\" /> Dashboard Inteligente de Predicciones\n            </h1>\n            <p className=\"text-neutral-500 text-xs mt-1 leading-relaxed\">\n              Modelos de Machine Learning entrenados en paralelo sobre la base de datos relacional <span className=\"text-amber-500 font-mono\">parrillero</span> de Laragon.\n            </p>\n          </div>\n\n          <div className=\"flex items-center gap-2\">\n            <button\n              onClick={fetchAnalysis}\n              className=\"flex items-center gap-1.5 bg-neutral-900 hover:bg-neutral-850 text-neutral-300 border border-neutral-800 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg text-xs font-semibold font-mono\"\n            >\n              <RefreshCw className=\"w-3.5 h-3.5\" /> Recalcular M\303\251tricas\n            </button>\n            <span className={`h-2.5 w-2.5 rounded-full ${dbStatus?.connected ? \"bg-green-500 animate-pulse\" : \"bg-yellow-500\"}`} />\n            <span className=\"text-neutral-500 text-[10px] font-mono\">\n              Status DB: {dbStatus?.connected ? \"Laragon Conectado\" : \"Usando Cloud Sync\"}\n            </span>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n\n        {/* Info Notification regarding Real-time Sync */}\n        <div className=\"bg-amber-950/20 border border-amber-900/40 rounded-xl p-5 mb-8 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-start gap-4\">\n          <Sparkles className=\"w-6 h-6 text-amber-500 shrink-0 mt-0.5\" />\n          <div>\n            <h3 className=\"font-bold text-amber-500 text-sm\">\360\237\222\241 \302\277C\303\263mo se actualiza este Dashboard en Tiempo Real al modificar Laragon?</h3>\n            <p className=\"text-neutral-400 text-xs mt-1 leading-relaxed\">\n              <strong>El Procedimiento T\303\251cnico:</strong> Cuando el due\303\261o a\303\261ade compras directamente en HeidiSQL/Laragon, no se requiere reescribir ni recompilar la p\303\241gina web. \n              El frontend se comunica con un backend din\303\241mico en Express que realiza la consulta SQL unificada por <code>JOIN</code> en segundos. Al llamar la API <code>/api/ml-analysis</code>, \n              pandas-like filters operan en tiempo real, re-entrenando instant\303\241neamente los algoritmos locales de <strong>\303\201rbol de Decisi\303\263n</strong> y <strong>KNN</strong> con los datos frescos y actualizando las proyecciones y el gr\303\241fico de vector interactivo en milisegundos.\n            </p>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n\n        {/* Dashboard Grid split */}\n        <div className=\"grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-8\">\n          \n          {/* Main Visualizers Panel (Left) */}\n          <div className=\"lg:col-span-8 space-y-6\">\n            \n            {/* Nav Filters inner tabs */}\n            <div className=\"flex items-center gap-2 border-b border-neutral-900 pb-3\">\n              <button\n                onClick={() => setActiveTab(\"visuals\")}\n                className={`px-4 py-2 rounded-lg text-xs font-semibold ${\n                  activeTab === \"visuals\" ? \"bg-amber-600 text-neutral-950\" : \"text-neutral-400 hover:text-neutral-200 hover:bg-neutral-900\"\n                }`}\n                id=\"btn-tab-visuals\"\n              >\n                Gr\303\241fico Vectorial & Visualizaciones\n              </button>\n              <button\n                onClick={() => setActiveTab(\"pandas\")}\n                className={`px-4 py-2 rounded-lg text-xs font-semibold ${\n                  activeTab ==